headline: Howmet Aerospace Board Approves Common Stock Dividend
summary: The Board of Directors of Howmet Aerospace Inc. (NYSE: HWM) declared a dividend of 12 cents per share on the outstanding Common Stock of the Company, to be paid on November 25, 2025, to the holders of record of the Common Stock at the close of business on November 7, 2025.
